    {
      "time": 72.747,
      "text": "These atoms have travelled from a distant star in time to be there for the birth of the solar system, and then they hit the Earth in an impact which left a golden signature on our landscape.",
      "translation": "这些金原子最早来自遥远的恒星，穿越漫长时空，见证了太阳系的诞生，随后又随着一次撞击来到地球，在这颗星球的地表留下了金色的印记。",
      "words": [
